{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"lighting-color","mdn_url":"/ru/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/lighting-color","locale":"ru","native":"Русский","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"Справочник SVG атрибутов\">Справочник SVG атрибутов</a></p>\n\n<p>Атрибут <code>lighting-color</code> определяет цвет источника света для примитивов фильтров  <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feDiffuseLighting\"><code>&lt;feDiffuseLighting&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> и <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpecularLighting\"><code>&lt;feSpecularLighting&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"контекст_использования","title":"Контекст использования","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Категория</th>\n   <td>Атрибут представления</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Значение</th>\n   <td>currentColor | <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#color\" title=\"en/SVG/Content_type#Color\">&lt;color&gt;</a> | <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#icccolor\" title=\"en/SVG/Content_type#ICCColor\">&lt;icccolor&gt;</a> | inherit</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Начальное значение</th>\n   <td>white</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Анимация</th>\n   <td>Да</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Нормативный документ</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/filters.html#LightingColorProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"примеры","title":"Примеры","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"элементы","title":"Элементы","isH3":false,"content